  "title": "Delivery Driver / Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2200 - $2500 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Central</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days: Monday to Friday</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 8:30am to 5pm</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Deliver items to different addresses and through different routes</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Load, unload, prepare, inspect, and operate delivery vehicle</strong></li>\n  <li>Pick, prepare, check, and complete orders for delivery or collection, promptly and accurately and place them in the correct sections</li>\n  <li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimum GCE ‘O’ level or equivalent qualification with at least 1 year of relevant experience</li>\n  <li><strong>Possess valid Class 3 / 4 driving license</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
